(52757, 134575, 0, 1, 'One day(Demo)', '', '2012-08-15 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 1, 'One day\r\nHey don’t sleep just come awke keep running\r\nHow long the risk would be end\r\nYou follow me our treasure buried out there\r\nThe burning red flame just we are\r\nOne day  I’m going to change\r\nOne day  I will win on everybody\r\nOne day  I’m doing everything\r\nin order to achieve our dream\r\nThis road to the success I know it won’t  go straight\r\nI just do my best to face everything\r\nBecause there are no more reason for me say go back\r\nFinal what do time will bring it\r\nRight now I just wanna say   let it all  let it all out\r\nStretch your hand  hold me now\r\nlet’s get the show and than prove yourself tonight\r\nSee  it   today''ll be my day\r\nI ganna take it out\r\nI try so hard all day I’m not for sure to get\r\nI trust all my faith and keep going\r\nHave you ever feel so sad and feel giving up\r\nI know but no more\r\n', '', 251, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-08-15 21:36:37', '2015-03-12 13:55:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
